title: Justice Leagues Pack (2001|Digital|OkC.O.M.P.U.T.O.-Novus-HD)
description:
Promotional info from ComicVine - "Alien invaders use Hector Hammond to make the world forget that the Justice League of America had ever existed, only to find the individual members of the Justice League instinctively creating new crime-fighting organizations beginning with the "Justice League of A" to fill the void."

This is six issues of the story arc (all but the Secret Files and Origins issue), which includes:
-Justice Leagues - JL (2001-03) 01 (digital) (OkC.O.M.P.U.T.O.-Novus-HD)
-Justice Leagues - Justice League of Aliens (2001-01) 01 (digital) (OkC.O.M.P.U.T.O.-Novus-HD)
-Justice Leagues - Justice League of Amazons (2001-03) 01 (digital) (OkC.O.M.P.U.T.O.-Novus-HD)
-Justice Leagues - Justice League of America (2001-03) 01 (digital) (OkC.O.M.P.U.T.O.-Novus-HD)
-Justice Leagues - Justice League of Arkham (2001-03) 01 (digital) (OkC.O.M.P.U.T.O.-Novus-HD)
-Justice Leagues - Justice League of Atlantis (2001-01) 01 (digital) (OkC.O.M.P.U.T.O.-Novus-HD)

All issues are digital copies done by OkC.O.M.P.U.T.O.-Novus in HD format. Thanks to them for their efforts, please seed and enjoy! :-)
